review:
They have qualified doctors and super easy appointment bookings. 
For last 5 yrs I was visiting various doctors to get treated. Finally visited here and got results. Dr. Rupali is a great IVF doctor who was always available whenever I needed help. She takes off the mental as well as financial burden.
Super satisfied!

It was a critical issue. I was not able to conceive for last 6 years. Got lot of medications and went for an ivf cycle in some other center. Finally after consulting with doctor rupali i underwent 3 months treatment and conceived. I would highly suggest her if you are facing any issues related to fertility.

Dr. Rupali was very patient and explained to us everything in extreme detail. We got the one thing that we were missing with other doctors - her time and undivided attention. We were extremely happy with the end result in the first attempt with her. Strongly recommend her for your IVF journey.

Was wanting to concieve from quite a long time. Had already visited many doctors for the same. Had 2 failed ivf attempts in the past and was very disheartened.  Then heard about Pristyn and Dr. Rupali. Thought of giving ourselves 1 more chance and meet her. She was very patient and stayed with us for the whole journey,  explained us in details and we had a successful ivf in 1st attempt with her and pristyn team. Thanks for giving us this joy...

review: Was facing conceiving problem due to my irregular periods. Dr helped me to treat the issue and we were finally able to conceive after a successful ivf treatment.

Dr Rupali is an excellent ivf specialist who helped me to decrease my financial and mental burden. She was always there when I needed help. I was having few complications but after almost 2 and half month treatment was able to conceive through ivf.
Was not able to conceive after treatments from different places. Then Dr Rupali helped me to conceive after a set of treatments. Will be forever grateful to the ivf doctor rupali and her team.

The process Dr Rupali follows is just awesome. She helped me to conceive after 2 months of treatment which was unbelievable based on my past test results. Would suggest her to everyone who is facing fertility issues.
Was tensed for so long but after Dr Rupali went through my reports i was assured to go for ivf and ultimately it worked. Dr Rupali is an excellent ivf specialist who helped me to ease my burden.
Was earlier trying medicines but with no result. But Dr Rupali and her team helped us to get pregnant in first attempt. She is a great ivf doctor.
